            <p class=" font-inter_regular text-black text-xs sm:text-sm xl:text-base ">Pay-Per-Click, a model of internet marketing in which advertisers pay a fee each time one of their ads is clicked. Essentially, it’s a way of buying visits to your site, rather than attempting to “earn” those visits organically. Some of the most popular PPC forms are:</p>
