                    <h3 class="font-inter_semibold text-black text-xs sm:text-sm xl:text-base mb-2 md:mb-2.5 lg:mb-4">Google Ads (Search/Youtube Campaigns) :</h3>
                    <p class="font-inter_regular text-black text-xs sm:text-sm xl:text-base">Being the boss of all search engines, needless to say google enjoys the utmost popularity of the web visitors. Google Adwords is the way you can make your advertisement appear among the sponsored section in Google searches, while your potential customers are searching for products like yours specifically. Meanwhile, youtube lets you provide video ads to your target audience when they are casually browsing the youtube videos.</p>

                </li>
