                    <p class="font-inter_regular text-black text-xs sm:text-sm xl:text-base">LinkedIn is a networking platforms for professionals and businesses. Unlike face book where the crowd is mostly casual, LinkedIn is a professional platform. It's all about businesses and careers. So, if you're looking to build business connections or earn some B2B clients, LinkedIn ads are a good way to go.</p>

